    <item>
      <title>美国石油的新涌入压低了欧洲原油价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/fresh-gush-of-us-oil-drives-down-the-price-of-crudes-in-europe</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国石油出口的新一轮激增再度压低了从欧洲到西非的原油实物价格，在需求旺季即将到来之际，这给消费者带来了潜在的安慰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/fresh-gush-of-us-oil-drives-down-the-price-of-crudes-in-europe</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
