      <title>监管机构考虑豁免股息税，香港股市上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港股市上涨，据称监管机构正在考虑一项提议，免除个人投资者通过沪港通购买的股票所赚取的股息税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/hong-kong-stocks-rise-as-regulators-consider-dividend-tax-waiver</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 01:37:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟企业对中国投资的兴趣降至历史最低点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/eu-firms-appetite-for-china-investment-sinks-to-record-low</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国欧盟商会的一项调查显示，随着企业寻求规避地缘政治风险并转向东南亚和欧洲，中国作为最佳投资国的地位正在丧失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-10/eu-firms-appetite-for-china-investment-sinks-to-record-low</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
